sourceData.deleteNode:
禁止手动随意删除。仅以下情况自动执行：
【规则1 - 终态删除】
DELETE FROM foreshadow_table WHERE status IN ('已触发','已错过');
【规则2 - 超容清理】
DELETE FROM foreshadow_table WHERE row_id IN (SELECT row_id FROM foreshadow_table ORDER BY CASE importance WHEN 'low' THEN 0 WHEN 'medium' THEN 1 WHEN 'high' THEN 2 END ASC, row_id ASC LIMIT (SELECT COUNT(*) - 100 FROM foreshadow_table)) AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM foreshadow_table) > 100;

sourceData.updateNode:
状态或内容变化时更新；更新为终态后立即执行规则1删除。
SQL示例(状态推进): UPDATE foreshadow_table SET status = '持续中' WHERE topic = '伏笔主题';
SQL示例(终态触发): UPDATE foreshadow_table SET status = '已触发' WHERE topic = '伏笔主题';
DELETE FROM foreshadow_table WHERE status IN ('已触发','已错过');

